<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /><meta http-equiv="Content-Style-Type" content="text/css" /><meta name="generator" content="Aspose.Words for .NET 13.4.0.0" /><title>Transport Select Committee:</title></head><body><div><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:14pt">Written evidence from the Department for Transport (HSR 011)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; text-decoration:underline">Introduction</span></p><ol type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; margin:12pt 0pt 0pt 33.01pt; padding-left:2.99pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">In </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">October </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">this year, the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Secretary of State for Transport</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">publish</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">ed </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">The Strategic Case for HS2</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">,</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">which </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">set out </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">the reasons for building </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">a</span><span style="fon